# Project core

- **Stack:** Next.js 16 (frontend) + Go/chi/pgx (masterfabric-go) + Docker hybrid MLC/Grafana.
- **Live:** Vercel + Render + Cloudflare tunnel to local MLC/Grafana — treat as production.
- **Privacy:** User reviews and decisions are per-account in Postgres; do not log secrets or raw tokens.
- **Language:** Code comments, commits, PR titles/bodies in **English**. Chat may be Turkish.
- **MCP:** Deferred until explicitly requested — keep REST analyze path working.

```text
✅ Frontend-only UI → no API break for live
✅ Backend changes → go build + existing route compatibility
❌ Commit .env.hybrid / tunnel tokens / Render secrets
```
